<br>
Time stopped. <br>
<br>
'what is this?' i wonder.<br>
'what has happened?' I can't breathe,i can't see for that matter.<br>
<br>
I feel like i'm being pulled away. <br>
<br>
I wish this feeling would stop,I really don't like it. <br>
<br>
I wish who ever is doing this would stop.<br>
<br>
I want them to just go away.<br>
<br>
just GO AWAY.<br>
<br>
<br>
Liz opens her eyes slowly and looks around. A surprised Win stands off to the side and a boy lies crumbled at the bottom of a large mech. Liz rubs her throat carefully,it feels like somebodys' been trying to choak her. She looks up at Win.<br>
<br>
&quot;what just happened?&quot;<br>
He answers slowly,&quot;you just threw that guy into that machine,&quot; win gulps slightly,&quot;without touching him,&quot;<br>
&quot;how...how could i do something like that?&quot;<br>
