<br>
Well well well,here comes another into the fray. Things were getting out of hand here,first theres this big storm,then the creatures land,next comes so pysco in a mech followed by some guy with a big gun and a glowing mask. Whats the world coming too?<br>
<br>
  Liz shook her head. Things couldn't get any weirder could they? She stood up to her full height,which was only a mere 5'3,standing up on her toes as best to look this new person in the eye. She squinted her eyes ,placed her hands on her hips and gave him an acusing stare.<br>
&quot;so..who are you? Another type of alien that landed here just for the fun of it? Because to the best of my knowledge no on this planet has a mask,weapons or hair like that,&quot; She lowered herself back down to her normal height and crossed her arms.<br>
